 For media :

  only an image uploaded - header.png or header.jpg : this image will be displayed in the header
  an image and a video - poster.png or poster.jpg and header.mp4 : the video will be displayed, and the image will be the poster
  only a video - header.mp4 : the video will be displayed, no poster
  thumbnail.png : will be the project thumbnail on the home. If not present, will use header.png/jpg or poster, else cw4.png

