   put in expert mode > frontmatter

    video-pause (true false)
    video-mute (true false)
    play-once (true false)
    banner-align (top, center, bottom, etc)
    splash-description (text)
    panorama-longitude-speed: (float)
    panorama-user-control: (true false)

